      <table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="5" width="85%">
        <tr> 
          <td colspan="3" bgcolor="#eeeeee" align="right"> 
            <font size="1">Photos UCAH/ Giovani Diffidenti</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/shellhole.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/shellhole_small.jpg" alt="shellhole.jpg (49126 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">1. Conditions 
              for civilians in Angola have steadily deteriorated throughout almost 
              30 years of a conflict which has killed close to a million people.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/womaninidpshelter.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/womaninidpshelter_small.jpg" alt="womaninidpshelter.jpg (43820 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">2. UN 
              Under Secretary-General for Humanitarian Affairs, Sergio Vieira 
              de Mello, has said there now are currently 1.7 million people displaced 
              by the war. </font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/boywithtank.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/boywithtank_small.jpg" alt="boywithtank.jpg (50698 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">3. A UN-brokered 
              interim peace agreement between the government and UNITA rebels 
              collapsed last December.</font> 
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/foodaidqueue.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/foodaidqueue_small.jpg" alt="foodaidqueue.jpg (34512 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">4. The 
              renewed fighting caused an estimated 700,000 people to flee to the 
              government-held cities of Kuito, Huambo and Malanje. But poor security 
              has frustrated the humanitarian community's efforts to help those 
              most badly affected.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/minefield.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/minefield_small.jpg" alt="minefield.jpg (42546 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">5. Nearly 
              all aid reaching Kuito, Huambo and Malanje has to be flown in to 
              the besieged cities at considerable expense because roads are too 
              dangerous to travel.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/boywaitingforfood.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/boywaitingforfood_small.jpg" alt="boywaitingforfood.jpg (33479 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">6. But 
              only a fraction of what people need can be guaranteed to get through.</font> 
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/beans.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/beans_small.jpg" alt="beans.jpg (40374 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">7. The 
              scarcity of food has inflated basic commodity prices far beyond 
              the means of ordinary people.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/drought.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/drought_small.jpg" alt="drought.jpg (40034 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">8. Households 
              that were barely coping are now completely dependant on humanitarian 
              assistance to survive.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/womanondrip.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/womanondrip_small.jpg" alt="womanondrip.jpg (48009 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">9. Health 
              services in the besieged cities are at an almost complete standstill.</font> 
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/womanbreastfeeding.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/womanbreastfeeding_small.jpg" alt="womanbreastfeeding.jpg (44416 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">10. Humanitarian 
              agencies in collaboration with the government have launched a child 
              vaccination campaign to ensure basic childhood illnesses, such as 
              polio, are controlled.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/womanwithchild.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/womanwithchild_small.jpg" alt="womanwithchild.jpg (42780 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">11. But 
              surgical care facilities lack drugs, trained staff, electricity 
              and even clean water.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/schoolclass.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/schoolclass_small.jpg" alt="schoolclass.jpg (49534 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">12. Education 
              services have also almost completely ground to a halt, effectively 
              denying today's children any opportunity for a better future.</font> 
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/deminer.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/deminer_small.jpg" alt="deminer.jpg (48292 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">13. Land 
              mines are another hazard facing civilians. But often desperate people 
              have no choice but to risk life and limb by venturing beyond safe 
              city limits to search for food and firewood.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/minevictim.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/minevictim_small.jpg" alt="minevictim.jpg (43050 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">14. There 
              is no official figure for the number of civilians maimed by mines 
              and unexploded ordinance in Angola's war, however, almost every 
              community has been touched by sudden tragedy.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/idpgroup.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/idpgroup_small.jpg" alt="idpgroup.jpg (46707 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">15. Assistance 
              programmes are dependant on limited donor funding. But appeals for 
              Angola have been increasingly poorly supported.</font> 
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/womenwashing.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/womenwashing_small.jpg" alt="womenwashing.jpg (50637 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">16. The 
              strain of constant war is visible everywhere in Angola's besieged 
              cities.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/motherwithsickchild.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/motherwithsickchild_small.jpg" alt="motherwithsickchild.jpg (34429 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">17. The 
              psychological and social trauma of the conflict is almost immeasurable.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/waiting.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/waiting_small.jpg" alt="waiting.jpg (25833 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">18.
              Meanwhile, Angolans say their plight has been largely forgotten 
              by the outside world.</font> 
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/peopleonthemove.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/peopleonthemove_small.jpg" alt="peopleonthemove.jpg (48382 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">19. Nevertheless, 
              there is little sign that the government and UNITA are any closer 
              to a negotiated end to the conflict.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/maninfrontofshelter.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/maninfrontofshelter_small.jpg" alt="maninfrontofshelter.jpg (50573 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a> 
           <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">20. But 
              humanitarian agencies say the world cannot continue to ignore Angola's 
              misery.</font> 
          </td>
          <td valign="top" align="center"><A href=# onClick="OpenNewWindow('angolaUCAH/boyonstairs.jpg','width=420,height=360');return false;"><img src="angolaUCAH/boyonstairs_small.jpg" alt="boyonstairs.jpg (36124 bytes)" border="1" width="100" height="75"></a>
            <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="1" color="#000000">21. One 
              aid worker told IRIN: &quot;The international community must do 
              more to stop the warlords and give ordinary people some chance for 
              peace&quot;.</font> 
          </td>
        </tr>
